The '''''Chandrila''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|Corellian Corvette]] in service to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was part of a task force commanded by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Ackbar]] during the [[Battle of Ciutric]]. It shared its name with the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]].

